WeaponType.Name: Knight's Sword
WeaponType.FlavorText: "He was wearing his fine white coat of mail and his helmet with gold-studded stones; by his side hung Joyeuse, and never was there a sword to match it; its colour changed thirty times a day."

WeaponType.Name: Battle Hammer
WeaponType.FlavorText: Judgement, a final sigh. Here, the screams electrified.

WeaponType.Name: Battle Hammer
WeaponType.FlavorText: The Hammer of Justice is the key to the future. The Bringer of Sorrow is the last you'll see.
